24.3 using the kickstart file for automatic installations

typically this file is provided on an installation server

before starting the installation, the client needs to indicate where to get the kickstart file from

	use ks=http://somewhere/ks.cfg
	or provide the interface provided by the installation program
	
at the installation prompt, select the install option and hit the tab key. You can add the ks=http://myserver/ks.cfg here. 